         </div>
         <div class="collection_v3-left">
           <div class="top_section_banner">
           <h5 class="Featured_coll_heading">Featured </h5>
             <button type="button" class="btn_collection_banner">$100 OFF for limited time only </button>
           </div>
            <h2>Wireless Outdoor Camera V3 </h2>
            <ul class="collection_outer_inner">
               <li class=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0249/8949/9437/files/collection_4g.png?v=1654540905" class="wireless_media_inner"><span> Connects on <br>4g networks</span></li>
